{"tid":513020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★公屋王變垃圾屋 鳳德邨單位疑錄音機短路起火","createTime":"2017-12-29T06:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T06:55:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"292691fddf0baee4f563c730a47a2ffdf2a52a20","tid":513020,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時左右，黃大仙鑽石山鳳德邨雪鳳樓一個住宅單位突然發生火警，消防接報後趕至現場，開喉將火救熄，同時救出單位內一對母子。據悉，獲救母親姓林，已屆95歲高齡；兒子姓葉，亦已67歲，他們均吸入濃煙不適，由救護車送院治理。現場消息稱，涉事單位相信是「垃圾屋」，屋內佈滿雜物凌亂不堪。初步懷疑一部陳年錄音機疑短路冒煙，附近雜物被波及起火，導致火警，相信火警起因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/145033/-%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%B1%8B-%E9%99%B3%E5%B9%B4%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%E6%A9%9F%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB%E7%87%92%E9%9B%9C%E7%89%A9-%E5%B9%B4%E9%82%81%E6%AF%8D%E5%AD%90%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E6%BF%83%E7%85%99%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F145033%2F-%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%258C%2584%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2587%2592%25E9%259B%259C%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2582%2581%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25BF%2583%25E7%2585%2599%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%25A9%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDikm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=686de612\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/145033/-%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%B1%8B-%E9%99%B3%E5%B9%B4%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%E6%A9%9F%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB%E7%87%92%E9%9B%9C%E7%89%A9-%E5%B9%B4%E9%82%81%E6%AF%8D%E5%AD%90%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E6%BF%83%E7%85%99%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2</a>"},{"pid":"1116b4556bb3917c2b0ca834a8396d569e720b27","tid":513020,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/18433_%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht